title: [FLAC] Prince - Prince, Josh & Cora (2007 aftershow)
description:
Recorded live at indigo2, London on 29th August 2007 at 1am.

This is the best quality version of this show circulating ... by a very long way. Sourced from two brand new recordings, this matrix mix is as close to soundboard as you can get get.

The show itself is guitar, drums and bass - that&#039;s it. It rocks. Hard.
